物，只要人民反對，注定下台，此等人類文化遠超你所謂5千年的文化， 絕對不容置疑。<br />\n所以，沒有所以，因為原因都不關你狗共屁事。"},{"pid":"6221cae39156323749a1f87a4622bc22828141b8","tid":1514891,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"同支那講合約精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8635b45111db479fdf7a65b1e83f9d2222fc4b6d","tid":1514891,"uid":88663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cmab.gov.hk/mobile/gb/issues/jd2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmab.gov.hk%2Fmobile%2Fgb%2Fissues%2Fjd2.htm&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTCNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=fd75680c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cmab.gov.hk/mobile/gb/issues/jd2.htm</a><br />\n睇到第二同第三，支那已經違反咗啦"},{"pid":"f2d4dfd5fdfd4bef861746cdf25c4f30eedbb2b5","tid":1514891,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:56:57.000Z","msg":"呢份野就算啦"},{"pid":"03a85b293c972d245498127b9ce02bdee4cce7dc","tid":1514891,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf24a5cdec8f9e9b27c2e120cbf66a893bf02235","tid":1514891,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"過時<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無效<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff4417dceab2c43ebc302946636e688e0648a0d","tid":1514891,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf508e2044f609896191ee9f0851bbaff5de42b","tid":1514891,"uid":12628,"li